{ We've implemented the Important lines feature in this course. Concretely, we've marked about a third of the total number of lines as important based on their popularity according to both the Mega and Lichess databases and instructive value. These variations can be clearly distinguished by their title in bold.  You can activate the Learn Important Only feature on the course options menu. To make sure all the key moves work, you should then select the option Study all moves instead of Study key moves.  However, we recommend not activating these options and, instead, going through all the variations first and then using the bold titles as a reference throughout the study of this course. You can pause all the non-bold lines plus anything else you don't find relevant. This allows you to tailor the course to your preferences/level and maximize the efficiency in reviewing/memorizing the lines you deem most useful. }
