[FEN "r1bqkb1r/1ppp1ppp/p1n5/4p3/B3n3/5N2/PPPP1PPP/RNBQR1K1 b kq - 0 6"]
[SetUp "1"]

Nc5
{ Similar to the way in with ...Nd6 in the Berlin hits the Bishop on b5, here ...Nc5 wins the Bishop pair by attacking the Bishop on a4. The game may continue: }
7. Bxc6 dxc6 8. d4 Ne6 9. Nxe5 Be7
{ when Black is fine due to his two Bishops. } *

[Event "?"]
