[SetUp "1"]

7... d5 { Black stakes a claim in the centre and solidifies his Knight on e4. }
8. dxe5 Be6 { He further stabilizes his position by defending the d5 pawn. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
