[SetUp "1"]

12... d4 { This frees Black's position and gives him at least equality. } 13.
cxd4 Nxd4 14. Nxd4 Qxd4 15. Nf3 Qxd1 16. Rxd1 Rad8
{ Black has a comfortable ending here. } *

[Event "?"]
