13... c5
{ This pawn structure is reminiscent of the French Defense, and some of the same ideas do come into play. In this case Black challenges the base of White's pawn chain, while also hinting at ...c4 should White not take on c5. }
14. dxc5 Bxc5 { Black is totally fine here. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
