Nxc5 Rxb2
{ 24...Rxe3  has been played more often, intending to grab the  e5  pawn afterwards, but my gut tells me to get rid of the outside pawn. }
25. Nxa6 h6
{ Black is totally fine here. White's extra pawn is not worth much as it should not be possible to make a passer with this pawn structure. }
