{ Black takes control over the d4 square and is ready to drop a knight on this central outpost. The game is level.   An illustrative line goes  18.Rfd1  Nbd4  19.Nxd4  cxd4  20.Bxd4  Nxd4  21.Qe3  Nc2  22.Rxd8  Rfxd8  23.Qc1  Nxa1  24.Qxa1  Rd5  25.f4  Rd4  26.Qc1  Rad8=  with a likely draw. }
