{ The immediate pawn break is Black's most ambitious continuation. } 11. Bxe6
{ is by far White's main move, currently more than three times as popular as the alternatives. }
11... Nxe6 12. cxd4 Ncxd4 13. a4
{ Undermining the queenside is White's most common option. } 13... Bb4 14. axb5
