{ This is a rare but interesting line. What is Black's best move? } 11... Nxe5
{ This pawn grab is not normally possible, but tactically, it works out here.  The problem with   11...Nxd4?!  is that White has yet to commit his Knight to d2, meaning f2-f3 will chase the e4-Knight back to an awkward square, as there is no option to exchange it. }
