{ Black intends ...Qb7 to attack d5. We have some advantage here, as the d-pawn is weak, we have two Bishops, and a strong Knight on e5 which can only be ejected with the weakening f2-f4. ...Bf6 and a Rook to the e-file is a likely follow-up to this Queen maneuvre. }
